Help file: commands
.
Commands in cmdOS
.
	cmdOS has commands. You can view all commands by
	typing 'list' or 'help'
.
 Lets view standart commands
.
	clear - This command cleaning your command history 
	(cmdOS screen)
.
	list,help - Prints all commands
.
	exit - Exit from cmdOS
.
	reboot - Reopening session
.
	howto - Opens howto program
.
	repair - Opens window where you can choose repair 
	file(s)
.
	ver - Displays version of cmdOS
.
	changes - Displays changes
.
.
.
